# The Oniro flavor HAPs are built on demand by build-oniro-haps.sh (cloned from
# the pinned remotes in oniro-haps.json) and are intentionally NOT committed.
# Eclipse release model: no published binaries; the consumer reproduces locally.
# Provenance lives in ../oniro-haps.json (committed); checksums in SHA256SUMS.
*.hap
SHA256SUMS
